49:47.751 --> 49:49.453 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I was born this way.

49:49.486 --> 49:53.123 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
I'm sure we could cut to
pictures of me right
now as a kid looking cute.

49:53.157 --> 49:56.026 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But we're going to cut back to
me.

49:56.060 --> 50:02.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
